data.description:
Everything on Your Wish List! 
Quality Kappert Construction, this Custom 3yr Old Home Offers an Open Concept w/Vaulted Ceilings, Wall of Windows, Hand Scraped Engineered Flooring & a Dream Kitchen w/Gorgeous 8ft. Island, Granite Counters, Custom Staggered Cabinetry, Upgraded SS Appliances, Pantry & More. Inviting Master Suite w/Vaulted Ceiling & Luxury Master Bath w/Dual Vanity, Sep. Tub &  Shower Plus Lg. Walk-In Closet. Two Additional Bds, Guest Bath & Laundry on Main Level. Fantastic 38ft Family Rm on Lower Level, Perfect for Entertaining w/Space for Pool Table ect. Fourth Bd, Bonus Rm & 3rd Full Bath, Nice! Unfinished Portion w/Abundant Storage Space. Oversized 3 Car Garage, Covered Patio & Lush Lawn Offering Great Curb Appeal.
